sequenceDiagram
  title seq_uc010_admin_usuarios — FSD-UC-010 Admin Usuarios y Materias
  actor AdminSistema as Admin. Sistema
  participant API as API SGAI
  participant DOM as Administracion Service
  participant SMTP as Cola Notificaciones
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  AdminSistema->>API: POST /admin/usuarios { nombre, email, rol, facultadId }
  API->>API: Verificar rol ADMIN_SISTEMA
  API->>DOM: crearUsuario(datos)
  DOM->>DOM: Validar Zod + email único
  DOM->>DOM: bcrypt hash password temporal
  DOM->>DB: INSERT usuario + auditoria
  DB-->>DOM: userId
  DOM->>SMTP: Encolar email bienvenida
  DOM-->>API: { userId, email }
  API-->>AdminSistema: 201 Created
